description: Data was loaded from the International Classification of Diseases for Oncology, 3rd Edition (ICD-O-3) published by the World Health Organization (WHO) in February 2019. More details: https://www.who.int/classifications/icd/adaptations/oncology/en/

fields.description: ICD-O-3 topology (aka primary site) code, 330 unique strings from C00.0 to C80.9
fields.name: topo_code

fields.description: ICD-O-3 topology label, 330 unique strings from External upper lip to Unknown primary site
fields.name: topo_label
